data.description: Nothing short of spectacular! This 5BD 6.5BA 5800+ sf Custom CONTEMPORARY home set on 1.5 acres was built-to-suit the builder himself. Features 4 garages, radiant heat HW floors, rooftop deck, covered patio overlooking backyard oasis w 20x40 pool, 10'-15' ceilings & floor to ceiling windows for tons of natural light. Expansive kitchen open to FR w FP & extra wide sliders to patio w outdoor FP. The kitchen inclds high-end SS appliances, lg center island w waterfall quartz countertops, lg pantry, butler pantry & 1st floor en-suite. 2nd floor houses to 3 en-suite BDs, palatial Master en-suite elegantly designed w arched ceiling, FP, huge WICs, luxurious BA w soaking tub, walk in shower, dual sinks & entrance to outdoor patio w FP, office & laundry. Finished basement w home theater, rec room w wet bar & full bath. HOME IS UNDER CONSTRUCTION and expected completion is Spring 2021.
